- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper proposes a new framework for managing concurrency using process calculi, which is related to programming languages. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses real-time capable systems for managing concurrency, which is related to systems and control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper mentions using machine improvisation, which is related to artificial intelligence.
